<section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-ochre-100 px-6 py-16 text-stone-900 shadow-xl shadow-stone-300/40 sm:px-10 lg:px-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,_rgba(201,129,61,0.16),_transparent_34%),radial-gradient(circle_at_left,_rgba(255,255,255,0.4),_transparent_28%)]"></div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto grid min-h-[calc(100vh-14rem)] max-w-6xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
    <div class="min-w-0 max-w-3xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-ochre-700">
        Screenshot Wishlist Organizer
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl">
        あの時の
        <span class="text-red-600">欲しい</span>
        を
        <span class="block">ちゃんと叶える。</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="mt-8 max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-base leading-8 text-stone-700 sm:text-lg">
        <p>
        SNSで見かけた「欲しいもの」、スクリーンショットのままで溜まっていませんか？
        </p>
        <p>
          このアプリでは、スクショ画像をアップするだけでAIが商品名やショップを読み取り、
          あなたの「欲しいもの」を自動でリスト化します。
        </p>
        <p>
          ショップごとにまとめてチェックできるから、実店舗でもオンラインでも、
          買い物がもっとスムーズに進みます。
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.18em] text-stone-600 sm:text-base">
        「欲しい」を、迷わず、後悔なく。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <%= link_to "ログイン",
            login_path,
            class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-amber-300/50 transition hover:bg-amber-600" %>
        <%= link_to "新規登録",
            new_user_path,
            class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-stone-900 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-stone-400/30 transition hover:bg-red-700" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="min-w-0 w-full rounded-[2rem] bg-stone-950 p-5 text-white shadow-2xl shadow-stone-400/25 sm:p-6" data-step-slider>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-stone-400">How It Works</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-2xl">3 STEPで整理する</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden items-center gap-2 sm:flex">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-stone-200 transition hover:bg-white/10"
            data-step-prev
          >
            PREV
          </button>
          <button
            type="button"
            class="rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-stone-200 transition hover:bg-white/10"
            data-step-next
          >
            NEXT
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mt-5 flex w-full snap-x snap-mandatory gap-4 overflow-x-auto pb-2 [scrollbar-width:none] [&::-webkit-scrollbar]:hidden"
        data-step-track
      >
        <article class="w-full min-w-full shrink-0 snap-center rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <span class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-red-600 text-sm font-bold text-white">01</span>
            <%= image_tag "step-sns-phone.svg",
                alt: "スマホに映るSNS投稿のイラスト",
                class: "h-28 w-28 rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover ring-1 ring-white/10" %>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-red-300">STEP 1</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">スクショを保存</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-300">
            気になった商品画像をそのままアップロード。保存した瞬間から整理の準備が始まります。
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="w-full min-w-full shrink-0 snap-center rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <span class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-500 text-sm font-bold text-white">02</span>
            <%= image_tag "step-share-send.svg",
                alt: "SNS情報を送信するイラスト",
                class: "h-28 w-28 rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover ring-1 ring-white/10" %>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-amber-300">STEP 2</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">AIが整理</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-300">
            商品名、ブランド、ショップ候補を自動抽出。あとから見返しやすい形へまとめます。
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="w-full min-w-full shrink-0 snap-center rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <span class="inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-emerald-600 text-sm font-bold text-white">03</span>
            <%= image_tag "step-shopping-check.svg",
                alt: "買い物とチェックマークのイラスト",
                class: "h-28 w-28 rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover ring-1 ring-white/10" %>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-emerald-300">STEP 3</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">買い物しやすく</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-300">
            ショップ別に見返せるので、店舗でもオンラインでも必要な情報へすぐ辿り着けます。
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 flex items-center justify-center gap-2" data-step-dots>
        <button type="button" class="h-2.5 w-8 rounded-full bg-red-500 transition" data-step-dot="0" aria-label="STEP 1へ"></button>
        <button type="button" class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-white/25 transition" data-step-dot="1" aria-label="STEP 2へ"></button>
        <button type="button" class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-white/25 transition" data-step-dot="2" aria-label="STEP 3へ"></button>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4 text-center text-xs tracking-[0.18em] text-stone-500">
        左へスワイプして次のSTEPを見る
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
